  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-technology\">high-energy beam weapon</span> for ship-to-ship combat. <br><br>Though vulnerable to <span class=\"name name-fuel\">overheating</span>, these highly accurate laser weapons can <span class=\"name name-stellar\">recharge the users's shields</span> by leeching energy from target shield systems.<br><br>Use <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span> to change weapon mode. Press <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span> to fire.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种舰对舰的<span class=\"name name-technology\">高能量光束武器</span>。<br><br>虽然很容易<span class=\"name name-fuel\">过热</span>，但这种高精准度的激光武器可以通过吸取目标护盾系统的能量来<span class=\"name name-stellar\">充能使用者的护盾</span>。<br><br>使用<span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span>变更武器模式。按下<span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span>发射。",
    "TencentChinese": "航天激光武器和小行星开采工具。<br><br>使用者请注意，必须用<span class=\"name name-fuel\">有机元素</span>给本设备充能。<br><br>按 <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span> 激活。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一種用於太空船作戰的<span class=\"name name-technology\">高能量光束武器</span>。<br><br>雖然容易<span class=\"name name-fuel\">過熱</span>，這些高精準度雷射武器可從目標防護罩系統中汲取能量，<span class=\"name name-stellar\">為使用者的防護罩充能</span>。<br><br>使用 <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span> 即可切換武器模式。按住 <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span> 即可開火。"
  },
  "Teach": true,
